dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Terry Henderson. May I have your name please?
Hi Terry, my name is Amber Kelly.
Great to meet you, Amber. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is nine eight seven six.
Thank you, Amber. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle?
Of course, I drive a two zero one seven Toyota Corolla.
Thank you for the information, Amber. How can I assist you today with Old Stone Auto Insurance?
I need to inquire about adding a new driver to my policy.
Understood, Amber. We can definitely help with that. Let's proceed with adding the new driver.
Thank you for bringing this to our attention, Amber. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Terry, for your help.
You're welcome, Amber. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
